{"tid":1062074,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"點解香港中學唔教d實用d既野","createTime":"2019-03-15T00:30:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-17T13:14:26.000Z","uid":107362,"like":494,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"81afaf72d67273f1c9774566a933c489723ced39","tid":1062074,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:30:19.000Z","msg":"例如點樣同人相處 <br />\n成熟的處事手法<br />\n培養一個好的性格<br />\nPolitics<br />\n-&gt;點做一個大人<br />\n<br />\n+點樣理財<br />\n+思考邏輯<br />\n+基本中英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家教埋d野全部都係空中樓閣 象牙塔 過時既學術野<br />\n上到大學全部無用<br />\n班友考完試就乜7都唔記得 因為現實根本用唔著<br />\n只係識食玩屌訓 <br />\n<br />\n英文仲抵死 小學教到中六 8成人畢業個陣連基本grammar 都未曉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下政府請好多位都只係要求中英文writing+個人presentable(外表+談吐）<br />\n<br />\n不過咁都好 機會留返比早d覺醒，早d預備既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d61ac04cfc72ed9ad7684b3bc8b8b10745c1661","tid":1062074,"uid":38267,"like":554,"dislike":4,"score":550,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T00:32:44.000Z","msg":"因為D老師都教唔到你依D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe71a1e50929b3c8bffd16aea68841a96737f921","tid":1062074,"uid":123848,"like":257,"dislike":3,"score":254,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"因為D教師都唔識"},{"pid":"89d402730d5b33ab06d8e75aa36f189543615845","tid":1062074,"uid":217748,"like":158,"dislike":9,"score":149,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:09:09.000Z","msg":"識就唔會做老師啦"},{"pid":"25af205b86df9d768b90acb9c2beb63e5ae28ea2","tid":1062074,"uid":107362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4aaf35c042d003d7a1346486f7dc3dc0508aaba","tid":1062074,"uid":48887,"like":130,"dislike":1,"score":129,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"教呢啲要考牌嘅話應該無左起碼七成嘅老師"},{"pid":"69828a793cd4700a470d5c78c5c